<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Theme-Usage on Arberia Theme</title><link>https://arberiatheme.netlify.app/categories/theme-usage/</link><description>Recent content in Theme-Usage on Arberia Theme</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Jun 2022 18:28:32 +0200</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://arberiatheme.netlify.app/categories/theme-usage/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Build in Shortcodes</title><link>https://arberiatheme.netlify.app/build-in-shortcodes/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 Jul 2022 08:53:46 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://arberiatheme.netlify.app/build-in-shortcodes/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;strong>Hugo&lt;/strong> provides multiple built-in shortcodes for author convenience and to keep your markdown content clean.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Hugo uses Markdown for its simple content format. However, there are a lot of things that Markdown doesn’t support well. You could use pure HTML to expand possibilities.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>But this happens to be a bad idea. Everyone uses Markdown because it’s pure and simple to read even non-rendered. You should avoid HTML to keep it as simple as possible.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Extended Shortcode</title><link>https://arberiatheme.netlify.app/extended-shortcode/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 May 2022 18:19:27 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://arberiatheme.netlify.app/extended-shortcode/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;strong>Arberia Theme&lt;/strong> provides multiple built-in shortcodes for author convenience and to keep your markdown content clean. To expand your possibility this is an example list of all provided shortcodes.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="alert">Alert&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Shortcode to inset varius alert on markdown post use this code:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{{&amp;lt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672">alert-info&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">&amp;#34;[**&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Click&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">here&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">to&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">get&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">an&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">example&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">of&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">info&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">alert&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">**](&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">https:&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">//&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">antedoro&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">.&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">it&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">/)&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">followed&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">in&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">this&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">tutorial&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">.&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{{&amp;lt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672">alert-success&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">&amp;#34;[**&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">Click&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">here&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">to&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">get&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">an&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">example&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">of&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">info&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">alert&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">**](&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">https:&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">//&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">antedoro&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">.&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">it&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">/)&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">followed&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">in&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">this&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">tutorial&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">.&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&amp;gt;}}
